data.description: No need to wait for new construction, this meticulously maintained Riverton Pointe beauty is move-in ready! Enjoy the relaxed luxury of Toll Bros. quality in a serene Lowcountry setting with this 3BR/3.5B one-story home on .29 acre lot. Large kitchen w/ granite, pull-outs, lots of prep & storage space plus 2023 Oven & Microwave. 2022 H2O Heater & Interior Paint. 2021 Roof & Furnace/Air Handler. Spacious bedrooms w/ en suites. Hardwood floors & smooth ceilings. Screened porch w/ sweeping lagoon view & shade trees. Pool, Fitness Center, Tennis & Pickleball, Jack Nicklaus Signature Golf Course, Cafe & more! Close to major routes/shopping/dining.
